{%- style -%}
  .section-{{ section.id }}-padding {
    padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top | times: 0.75 | round: 0 }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom | times: 0.75 | round: 0 }}px;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} {
    --pl-eco-ink: #153c37;
    --pl-eco-muted: #4f6c66;
    --pl-eco-accent: #bf6f1d;
    --pl-eco-border: rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.12);
    --pl-eco-cream: #f6f0e4;
    --pl-eco-surface: rgba(255, 251, 244, 0.92);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(191, 111, 29, 0.12), transparent 32%),
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(27, 94, 86, 0.14), transparent 40%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf3 0%, #f4ecdf 100%);
    color: var(--pl-eco-ink);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }}::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 2.4rem 2.4rem;
    opacity: 0.45;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__intro {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto 3.2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body-family, 'Sora', sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pl-eco-accent);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, 'Cormorant Garamond', serif);
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 6vw, 5.2rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__lead {
    max-width: 64rem;
    margin: 1.2rem auto 0;
    font-size: 1.65rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--pl-eco-muted);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-card,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__cluster-card,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-card {
    border: 0.1rem solid var(--pl-eco-border);
    border-radius: 2.2rem;
    background: var(--pl-eco-surface);
    box-shadow: 0 2rem 4.4rem rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.08);
    backdrop-filter: blur(0.8rem);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 2.4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.97), rgba(27, 94, 86, 0.92));
    color: #f8f5ee;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__label {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #f0c28d;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, 'Cormorant Garamond', serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4vw, 4.4rem);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-copy {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(248, 245, 238, 0.84);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-links,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__card-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 1.6rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-link,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__card-link,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, background-color 0.25s ease;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-link {
    min-height: 4.4rem;
    padding: 0 1.7rem;
    background: #f4c285;
    color: #153c37;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-link--ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: #f8f5ee;
    border: 0.1rem solid rgba(248, 245, 238, 0.28);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-link:hover,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__card-link:hover,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-0.2rem);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    align-content: start;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero-tags li {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 3.8rem;
    padding: 0 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 0.1rem solid rgba(248, 245, 238, 0.18);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    color: #f8f5ee;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__cluster-grid,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-grid,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guides-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.4rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__cluster-card,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card,
  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-card {
    padding: 2rem 1.8rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__kicker {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 2.8rem;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(191, 111, 29, 0.12);
    color: var(--pl-eco-accent);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__card-title {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, 'Cormorant Garamond', serif);
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: var(--pl-eco-ink);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__card-copy {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-size: 1.48rem;
    line-height: 1.72;
    color: var(--pl-eco-muted);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__card-link {
    min-height: 4rem;
    padding: 0 1.4rem;
    background: rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.06);
    color: var(--pl-eco-ink);
    border: 0.1rem solid rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.08);
    font-size: 1.28rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__card-link--guide {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: rgba(191, 111, 29, 0.22);
    color: var(--pl-eco-accent);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-shell {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.2rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-copy {
    max-width: 56rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-title {
    margin: 0.9rem 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, 'Cormorant Garamond', serif);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-text {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.72;
    color: var(--pl-eco-muted);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-grid {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    min-height: 100%;
    padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem 1.8rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 252, 246, 0.98), rgba(246, 238, 224, 0.94));
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6rem;
    height: 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(191, 111, 29, 0.95), rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.48));
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card .pl-eco__kicker {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card .pl-eco__card-title {
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card .pl-eco__card-copy {
    margin-top: 0;
    max-width: 28rem;
    font-size: 1.42rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card .pl-eco__card-links {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 1.1rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card .pl-eco__card-link {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: space-between;
    min-height: 0;
    padding: 1rem 1.35rem;
    border-radius: 1.6rem;
    background: rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.05);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-card .pl-eco__card-link--guide {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-shell {
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 251, 244, 0.96), rgba(247, 240, 228, 0.96));
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family, 'Cormorant Garamond', serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.08;
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-copy {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.38rem;
    line-height: 1.68;
    color: var(--pl-eco-muted);
  }

  .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guide-link {
    align-self: flex-start;
    min-height: 3.8rem;
    padding: 0 1.3rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: 0.1rem solid rgba(21, 60, 55, 0.14);
    color: var(--pl-eco-ink);
    font-size: 1.22rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .section-{{ section.id }}-padding {
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    }

    .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__hero {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.6fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    }

    .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__cluster-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-grid,
    .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guides-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 990px) {
    .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__support-shell {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.88fr) minmax(0, 1.12fr);
      align-items: start;
      gap: 2.2rem;
    }

    .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__cluster-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }} .pl-eco__guides-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }
{%- endstyle -%}

<section class="homepage-category-ecosystem-{{ section.id }}" aria-labelledby="CategoryMap-{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="page-width section-{{ section.id }}-padding pl-eco">
    <div class="pl-eco__intro">
      <p class="pl-eco__eyebrow">Featured categories</p>
      <h2 class="pl-eco__title" id="CategoryMap-{{ section.id }}">Start with the ingredients you use most.</h2>
      <p class="pl-eco__lead">Black pepper, cardamom, cloves, cinnamon, honey, coffee, and pantry staples chosen for everyday cooking that still smells alive when the pack opens.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pl-eco__hero">
      <article class="pl-eco__hero-card">
        <div>
          <p class="pl-eco__label">Spice first</p>
          <h3 class="pl-eco__hero-title">Fresh Kerala spices still lead the shelf.</h3>
          <p class="pl-eco__hero-copy">This is where Pureleven feels most like itself: pepper, cardamom, cinnamon, cloves, and useful bundles chosen for the moment aroma rises back into the kitchen.</p>
          <div class="pl-eco__hero-links">
            <a class="pl-eco__hero-link" href="/collections/all">Shop Kerala Spices</a>
            <a class="pl-eco__hero-link pl-eco__hero-link--ghost" href="/blogs/cooking-spices">Explore Ingredient Guides</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="pl-eco__hero-tags" role="list" aria-label="Primary spice entities">
          <li>Black Pepper</li>
          <li>Cardamom</li>
          <li>Cinnamon</li>
          <li>Cloves</li>
          <li>Combo Packs</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <nav class="pl-eco__cluster-grid" aria-label="Primary spice categories">
      <article class="pl-eco__cluster-card">
        <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Primary spice cluster</span>
        <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Black Pepper</h3>
        <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Bold, fragrant pepper from the hills of Kerala. Crack it fresh over curries, eggs, soups, and grilled dishes.</p>
        <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/collections/spiciest-black-pepper">Shop Black Pepper</a>
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/cooking-spices/spice-of-kings-kerala-black-pepper-varieties">Read the Pepper Guide</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="pl-eco__cluster-card">
        <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Primary spice cluster</span>
        <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Cardamom</h3>
        <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Naturally sweet and deeply aromatic. Good for chai, biryani, desserts, and the spice box you open every day.</p>
        <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/collections/export-quality-cardamom">Explore Cardamom</a>
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/cooking-spices/difference-between-green-and-black-cardamom">Read the Cardamom Guide</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="pl-eco__cluster-card">
        <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Primary spice cluster</span>
        <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Cinnamon</h3>
        <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Warm, fragrant bark chosen for cleaner sweetness and better balance in tea, baking, and everyday cooking.</p>
        <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/collections/cinnamon">Browse Cinnamon</a>
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/cooking-spices/spice-checklist-how-to-check-quality-of-spices">Read the Spice Checklist</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="pl-eco__cluster-card">
        <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Primary spice cluster</span>
        <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Cloves</h3>
        <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Whole cloves selected for warmth, depth, and the kind of kitchen aroma you notice as soon as they hit heat.</p>
        <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/collections/cloves">Browse Cloves</a>
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/cooking-spices/how-to-store-spices">Read the Storage Guide</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="pl-eco__cluster-card">
        <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Primary spice cluster</span>
        <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Combo Packs</h3>
        <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">An easier way to start a better spice shelf, whether you are restocking the kitchen or giving a useful gift.</p>
        <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/collections/combo">Shop Combo Packs</a>
          <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/cooking-spices/best-kerala-spice-brands-online-india">Read the Kerala Spice Guide</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </nav>

    <div class="pl-eco__support-shell">
      <div class="pl-eco__support-copy">
        <p class="pl-eco__eyebrow">Coffee, honey &amp; more</p>
        <h3 class="pl-eco__support-title">The wider pantry, kept simple.</h3>
        <p class="pl-eco__support-text">Honey, coffee, herbs, and pantry comforts belong here when they make everyday cooking smell better and feel more grounded.</p>
      </div>

      <nav class="pl-eco__support-grid" aria-label="Supporting ingredient categories">
        <article class="pl-eco__support-card">
          <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Supporting category</span>
          <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Raw Honey</h3>
          <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Unhurried sweetness with floral character and a pantry presence that feels closer to the source.</p>
          <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/blogs/honey">Discover Honey</a>
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/honey/ultimate-honey-purity-test-guide">Read the Purity Test</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="pl-eco__support-card">
          <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Supporting category</span>
          <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Coffee</h3>
          <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Coffee keeps the morning side of the pantry warm, bitter, and familiar without pulling focus from the spices.</p>
          <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/pages/coffee-page">Explore Coffee</a>
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/collections/products">Browse Pantry Products</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="pl-eco__support-card">
          <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Supporting category</span>
          <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Herbs</h3>
          <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Herb guides bring pairing ideas, everyday cooking rhythm, and a little more range to the shelf.</p>
          <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/blogs/herbs">Explore Herb Guides</a>
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/herbs/culinary-journey-with-aromatic-herbs">Read the Herbs Guide</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="pl-eco__support-card">
          <span class="pl-eco__kicker">Supporting category</span>
          <h3 class="pl-eco__card-title">Natural Foods</h3>
          <p class="pl-eco__card-copy">Tea, coffee, honey, and pantry staples round out the kitchen without crowding the spices.</p>
          <div class="pl-eco__card-links">
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link" href="/collections/products">Browse Natural Foods</a>
            <a class="pl-eco__card-link pl-eco__card-link--guide" href="/blogs/cooking-spices/how-to-store-spices">Read the Freshness Guide</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="pl-eco__guide-shell">
      <div class="pl-eco__support-copy">
        <p class="pl-eco__eyebrow">Kitchen reading</p>
        <h3 class="pl-eco__support-title">Ingredient Guides &amp; Kitchen Reading</h3>
        <p class="pl-eco__support-text">Learn how to choose better spices, store them well, compare varieties, and understand what freshness actually smells like in the kitchen.</p>
      </div>

      <nav class="pl-eco__guides-grid" aria-label="Popular ingredient guides">
        <article class="pl-eco__guide-card">
          <h4 class="pl-eco__guide-title">Why fresh spices smell stronger</h4>
          <p class="pl-eco__guide-copy">A farm-origin explanation for why fresher spices speak louder the moment they are opened.</p>
          <a class="pl-eco__guide-link" href="/blogs/cooking-spices/kerala-spices-farm-origin-vs-retail">Read the Farm-Origin Spice Guide</a>
        </article>

        <article class="pl-eco__guide-card">
